name: Based AI
additional_notices:
The following token has a variable tax function on the smart contract to change tax rates post deployment.
Do your own research and be careful if you are trading this token.

description.en:
What is the project about?
Based AI combines AI and Elon Musk meme culture to create a unique cryptocurrency. It utilizes AI algorithms to support smart trading and maximize returns.

What makes your project unique?
BAI Main Feature Points Community Driven & BSC Based Ecosystem We trust the power of the BSC ecosystem and believe our community. We will start as a meme token and continue as a AI platform. Join BAI community and Stay Safe

History of your project.
Our ai technology was inspired by Elon tweet

What’s next for your project?
We will be listed on several exchanges and looking forward to driving our usecase for mass adoption 

What can your token be used for?

Chapgpt and interactive ai technology
